Description:
You can support Cercica's mission in helping people with special needs by becoming a volunteer, who will contribute by: Accompanying young people and adults with special needs in activities during the week and in their free time;
Support and companionship for elderly people in their homes;
Support in educational gardens, greenhouses, and plant nurseries;
Fundraising and other one-off events (food collection, Pirilampo Mágico, etc.);
Provision of specialized services (marketing and communication, IT, multimedia, accounting, logistics, etc.).
